 <span data-ttu-id="b123e-366">此方法主要用于测试从服务器返回的`LOB`是否为 NULL, 如以下示例中所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b123e-366">This technique is used primarily to test whether a `LOB` returned from the server is NULL, as the following example illustrates.</span></span>  
  
```  
If(myLob == OracleLob.Null)  
